BCR_data_scripts

Scripts, metadata, intermediate processed data and figures for bulk and single-cell BCR analysis ################################################################################## The repository is divided in 3 sub-folders:

    bulk

This subfolder contains:

    the scripts, numbered from 1 to 3 to analyse the bulk BCR data
    the intermediate processed data utilized for the analysis and for the figures. This folder includes the clonotype tables of the bulk BCR data generated with MiXCR. In the file 200714_bulk_BCR.Rdata
    the generated figures

    single-cell

This subfolder contains:

    the scripts, numbered from 1 to 3 to analyse the bulk BCR data
    the intermediate processed data utilized for the analysis and for the figures
    the generated figures

    metadata

This subfolder contains the metadata files utilized for the analysis.
